  "content": " <div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"9391\" class=\"elementor elementor-9391\" data-elementor-settings=\"{&quot;ha_cmc_init_switcher&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\"> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-05e4759 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"05e4759\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b0fd53a\" data-id=\"b0fd53a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ee5f60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"9ee5f60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-eca2b68 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"eca2b68\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-55735ba\" data-id=\"55735ba\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af42f6c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"af42f6c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0f0f0f; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Urethral Discharge Syndrome</span></h2><blockquote style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 3pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Urethral discharge syndrome</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> is a </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">prevalent sexually transmitted infection (STI) among men, marked by purulent urethral discharge</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">with or without dysuria</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. </span></blockquote><p> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The amount of discharge varies depending on the causative pathogens as well as prior antibiotic treatment. </span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-834304f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"834304f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3533e43\" data-id=\"3533e43\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd59b29 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"fd59b29\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f6037ea elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f6037ea\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-20c47f1\" data-id=\"20c47f1\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00b9cef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"00b9cef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Clinical Presentation:</span></h4><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Chief Complaint</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Patients with this syndrome often complain of a discharge from the urethra. Mucus or pus at the tip of the penis; staining underwear</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Symptoms</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: They may have symptoms of burning sensation while passing urine and frequency of micturition. </span></li></ul><h5 style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Physical Examination:</span></h5><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Visual Inspection</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Examination might reveal a purulent discharge from the urethra. If the discharge is not readily seen, it may be necessary to milk the penis and massage it forwards before the discharge becomes visible. If the discharge is copious, do not milk or squeeze the penis.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prepuce Examination</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: If the patient is not circumcised, you should examine with the foreskin retracted so that you ascertain whether the discharge is from the urethra or from beneath the prepuce. </span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Discharge Characteristics</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: The discharge may range from frank pus to mucopurulent.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Case Definition</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Urethral discharge in men with or without dysuria.</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1bc6ad1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1bc6ad1\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-df0bd2a\" data-id=\"df0bd2a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-82c80cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"82c80cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>  <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"7570414357\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-df956f7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"df956f7\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8f68176\" data-id=\"8f68176\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e86f9c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2e86f9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Causes </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Common and Uncommon):</span></h4><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Neisseria Gonorrhoeae</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> and </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Chlamydia Trachomatis</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: This syndrome is commonly caused by Neisseria gonorrhoeae and Chlamydia trachomatis in over 98% of cases.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Other Infectious Agents</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Trichomonas vaginalis</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ureaplasma urealyticum</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, and </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mycoplasma spp</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mixed Infections</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Mixed infections especially of Neisseria gonorrhoeae and Chlamydia trachomatis occur</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b1838d5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b1838d5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-94b6eb7\" data-id=\"94b6eb7\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b10da9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"8b10da9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-layout-key=\"-6q+ef+1v-2m-h\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"2010257102\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-275addb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"275addb\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-96f5c3a\" data-id=\"96f5c3a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a0e1ac elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0a0e1ac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management:</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">All male patients with urethral discharge should be managed according to the syndromic chart.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9396 size-full\" src=\"/images/Urethral-Discharge-Flow-Chart-Updated.png\" alt=\"Urethral Discharge Flow Chart Updated\" width=\"707\" height=\"813\" srcset=\"/images/Urethral-Discharge-Flow-Chart-Updated.png 707w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Urethral-Discharge-Flow-Chart-Updated-600x690.png 600w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Urethral-Discharge-Flow-Chart-Updated-261x300.png 261w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 707px) 100vw, 707px\" /></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Medicines</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ceftriaxone 250 mg IM or Cefixime 400 mg single dose plus Doxycycline 100 mg every 12 hours for 7 days</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If partner is pregnant</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Substitute doxycycline with erythromycin 500 mg every 6 hours for 7 days or Azithromycin 1 g stat if available</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Treatment Procedure:</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Clinical Assessment:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Obtain a comprehensive medical history and conduct a thorough examination of the client.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If urethral discharge is not evident, perform urethral milking.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Retract the prepuce (if applicable) and examine for ulcers.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Comprehensive Treatment:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Treat both the patient and their sexual partners simultaneously.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Provide counselling on abstinence or emphasize condom use to prevent further transmission.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Medication:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Administer Ceftriaxone 250 mg intramuscularly (IM) or Cefixime 400 mg as a single dose.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prescribe Doxycycline 100 mg every 12 hours for a duration of 7 days.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For Pregnant Partners:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If the partner is pregnant, substitute Doxycycline with Erythromycin 500 mg every 6 hours for 7 days.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Alternatively, administer Azithromycin 1 g as a single stat dose if available.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Persistent Symptoms Despite Partner Treatment:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Investigate for the presence of ulcers under the prepuce.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If discharge or dysuria persists, repeat Doxycycline 100 mg every 12 hours for 7 days.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Administer Metronidazole 2 g as a single dose.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If Partners Were Not Treated Initially:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Restart the initial treatment regimen and ensure partners are treated simultaneously.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Comprehensive STD Case Management Package:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Education</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Emphasis on treatment compliance.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Condom Promotion</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Provision and demonstration of correct usage.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partner Notification</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Treatment for partners, whether symptomatic or not.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">HIV VCT Services:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Offer or refer when necessary.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fce5cd; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Continued Persistence of Discharge:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Administer Ceftriaxone 1 g IM.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If symptoms persist, consider referral for specialist management.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Counsel and educate all clients on:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Treatment compliance.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Condom use and provide condoms.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partner management.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Offer or refer for HIV VCT services if necessary.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Schedule a return visit.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Abstinence from sex till all symptoms have resolved.</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f35cbfd elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f35cbfd\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-820a84c\" data-id=\"820a84c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20dd97e elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"20dd97e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"1271890507\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-120de89 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"120de89\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e691af1\" data-id=\"e691af1\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fdfa448 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fdfa448\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ece23788-7fff-4002-1605-ebbe1ecea476\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Abnormal Vaginal Discharge Syndrome</span></span></h2><p></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e19e965 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"e19e965\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-48bace4\" data-id=\"48bace4\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b68fcdd elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"b68fcdd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>  <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"7570414357\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> <!-- .entry-content .clear --> ",
  "semester": "year-1-semester-1"
}